allComsRaw <- read_csv(file.path(basedir, "output", "allCommodities.csv")) %>% 
    filter(!(commodity %in% c("Petroleum oil, non-crude", "Soya-bean oil", "Barley", "Olive oil", "Uranium"))) %>% 
    mutate(commodity = ifelse(grepl("Petroleum", commodity), "Crude oil", commodity))
